message.body: Safe travels!
Thanks! I met this awesome dance troupe from philly! I got their card. We have to watch them perform in philly or nyc!!
Awesome! Are you in mn? God that makes me want to skip work!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Yes! Just landed :)
Who is picking you up?
I might be back in the cities tonight? Twins game was supposed to be tomorrow but gbo sent a text that hinted at tonight? Idk
Ah, huh. What are you doing today?
Mom, game is tonight so I will let u know what today's plan is
Mmk cool. Enjoy!
The air is nice here! Much more fall-y
I was thinking that, it's getting cool!
I am going to hang out with Jen in shakopee and then ride with her to the game. Keep u updated!
What kind of person do you list as a personal reference for an apt?
I did former employers, maybe a professor?
So a former employee that I've known for two years is ok?
Oh yeah! the apt application bullshit still doesn't really make sense to me...
Just got done with a reading with jen and it feels so good. U should check her out after the wedding. We need those moments in tough transitions right missy?
Fact. Man do I need one. Im freaking out about Philadelphia! I'm glad you have that time with her. I want to hear what she said?
Quick pull an angel card to see if I should go to school.
It was short but it was some good clarity. Sometimes I forget about that connection. K I'm going to pull a card for u
K missy, I focused real hard and felt energy from two piles so I pulled two cards
Moving forward fearlessly and positive thoughts create positive results
Wowza!
Is that a trick deck?
"Trick deck" - sounds like something someone like virge would call a sweety pie like u
Ewewwwweewww. Are there 'this is a bad decision' cards in there? Did every side get a fair chance?
Hahaha well I'm sure there are cards that could be on the other side. I mean mine were kicking up your heels, moon phases, and make a commitment.
Moon?
But I told my sis about your situation and she had pretty good insight
What she say?
Yeah which is SO crazy because just on Saturday I was being so weird and I said "must be a full moon" and someone said "actually it is...." - things r just
Easier to see.
Well between the flat tires, housing issues, family dynamic, etc, (FIRE) she thinks that u might be best starting anew. And that u do good creating your own
Space. I think we've both developed a really strong sense of our own sense of happiness and it can be so difficult to make that fit into our environment and
Social circles
Hmm yea. I want to hear more! Hah. Call me when you get a chance and DON'T FORGET what she said :)
I can tell u how it felt....just ride wit me
How's wedding stuff? Family holding up?
Yeah, everything is pretty calm...
How's jen?
I think she's ready to just have fun and be done - she said it's weird to not have anything to plan
Well im super excited. Switched out my nose ring for a diamante and am getting my hair cut. :)
Yipeeeee!!! I'm ready to be crazy/silly/eye-catching maniacs!
I have the easiest job in the family
Yayyy. I wonder who my din din table partners are. What's your job? Not being parents, best man, or the bride?
Well I'm your date and that's a big responsibility.
Juggling with u
Juggling FIRE
The job description is dead on! No speech, no responsibilities - manager of joy and backup crisis management. Impressing people with our cool
You should see the new shoes I got. Cool part covered. Anyone fun in the wedding party slash need another bridesmaid?
I think the point is to be so cool ppl assume you're in the party. It really is a job cut out for us :)

We're so cool we talk about how we need to manipulate people in order to think we are. But for real, I don't know how appropriate it is and I don't really hold myself to it anyway, so hit me up. I'll be in town Friday evening. There's a table top at the grooms dinner with my name on it.
Where is the g dinner btw?
Oh also Zach bases, guy from larkspur, talks to me all the time on Facebook and told me to contact him when I'm in town... Hahaha
Oh shizzzz
Let's make this real: "do you ALWAYS have to have fun???"
Yes and I need a road sign
And then we can put on fake braces and make a music video about CRAZY we are
Speaking of crazy. Sofies driving me there. We need to talk about that.
Put it on the list!
Does jen have a dj?
Yeah
Or I think brett bode is playing
Playing an instrument?
No he just made the playlist? Ipod?
Ahhhh. Well I want to dance. Not too crazy though. Hank and eileen! My mom! Though they'll leave soon enough.
Girl it's your job. You're gonna dance like it's your job. #fun
Depending. On the day I think it would be nice to go to the cowles center open house on sunday :)
Was this for someone else?
Nope! It's the new dance center in mpls - looks great!
Oh cool. The rogue period confused me :)
It's my ppl completing the arts scene in mpls - theater, music, studio art and now.... DANCE!
